<P ID="5"><VG-VBN>Led</VG-VBN> <PG>by</PG> <NG><HEAD>laboratory</HEAD> <HEAD>director Dr. Philip Boynton</HEAD></NG>, and <NG>his chief <HEAD>scientists</HEAD> <HEAD>Drs. 
