<VG-VBG>exploiting</VG-VBG> <NG>a unique <HEAD>quality</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG> <NG>these so-called</NG> "<NG><HEAD>prion</HEAD></NG> <NG>diseases"--that</NG>
