<P ID="6"><VG-VBN>Caused</VG-VBN> <PG>by</PG> <NG>infectious</NG>, <NG>deformed <HEAD>proteins</HEAD></NG> <VG>called</VG> <NG><HEAD>prions</HEAD></NG>, <NG><HEAD>illnesses</HEAD></NG>
