<NG><HEAD>1982</HEAD></NG>. <NG>He</NG> <VG>stated</VG> that <NG>mammalian <HEAD>cells</HEAD></NG> <VG>contain</VG> <VG-VBG>prion</VG-VBG> <NG><HEAD>proteins</HEAD></NG> <PG>of</PG>
