<HEAD>asymmetry</HEAD></NG>. <VG-VBG>Using</VG-VBG> <NG><HEAD>hamsters</HEAD></NG> and <NG><HEAD>mice</HEAD></NG> <PG>as</PG> <NG><CARDINAL>one</CARDINAL> <HEAD>example</HEAD></NG>, <NG>he</NG> <VG>claims</VG> <NG>the
